Syntax: chakra

Focuses your internal chi energy to activate the Chakra skill, simultaneously
healing your wounds and boosting your combat damage. This skill is available
to Monk and Martial Artist class characters.

Effects when activated:
  - Heals a portion of your hit points based on your Monk and Martial Artist
    class levels: approximately (Monk + Martial Artist levels) * 5-7 HP.
  - Applies a damroll bonus equal to (Monk + Martial Artist levels) * 5,
    lasting 1 combat round (2 rounds if you have Martial Artist levels).
  - Activates a 10-round cooldown preventing reuse.

The skill costs chi energy. If you have recently used chakra the cost
increases due to the cooldown penalty.

Requirements:
  - Must be in combat.
  - Must have chi available.
  - Must have the Chakra skill learned.

